      <title>塞尔维亚总统武契奇暗示马斯克曾与特朗普通话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/serbia-s-vucic-signals-musk-was-present-during-trump-call</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞尔维亚总统亚历山大·武契奇表示，埃隆·马斯克周日与唐纳德·特朗普进行了通话，并称他与美国当选总统的通话是“莫大的荣幸”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/serbia-s-vucic-signals-musk-was-present-during-trump-call</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 14:06:18 GMT</pubDate>
