    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨领导的政党同意在 2 月份提前举行德国大选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/german-lawmakers-agree-to-hold-federal-election-on-feb-23</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨领导的社会民主党与反对派议员达成协议，将在2月提前举行选举，这将为社民党与弗里德里希·梅尔茨领导的保守党之间的较量奠定基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/german-lawmakers-agree-to-hold-federal-election-on-feb-23</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 09:38:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱尔兰的哈里斯驳斥了首席执行官在聚会上的言论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/o-leary-s-election-comments-risk-backfiring-on-irish-premier</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞安航空控股有限公司首席执行官迈克尔·奥利里对教师在政府任职发表了有争议的言论，迫使总理西蒙·哈里斯在选举前几周采取防御措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/o-leary-s-election-comments-risk-backfiring-on-irish-premier</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 11:57:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>政府垮台后德国下一步该做什么？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/germany-s-government-collapsed-what-s-next-quicktake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨领导的德国执政联盟在其所属的中左翼社会民主党、关注气候问题的绿党和支持商业的自由民主党之间长达数月的内斗之后破裂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/germany-s-government-collapsed-what-s-next-quicktake</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 13:54:51 GMT</pubDate>
